                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-medium text-foreground">render-info</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Using RendererInfo in Blazor</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-blue-400">
                        Blazor
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-3">
                    Documentation for using the <code>RendererInfo</code> class to detect rendering context:
                </p>
                <ul class="grid gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-foreground"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                        Detecting interactive vs static rendering
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-foreground"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
